<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l14">ein <expan>anſtellu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / der <expan>anlangu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l15">vnd <expan>gut<ex>en</ex></expan> von der ſteẅr <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> yecʒ beſchehen / beredt haben / hat </ab>
